ygData.messageBody:
Correction. Garren, Yiyang, Leschrec, Ziltus are the 20+level players.

Out of 4, Garren is the richest, u can borrow money is from him.
Yiyang, as a monk, dun need stuffs, try to strip him naked when u see him.
Leshrec, as a pure nuking machine, must respect him.
Ziltus, the weakest of 4, pls take care of him, help him, sayang him, give him all the goodies.

HAHHAHAHAAH! ;P
